  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2399148486?book_show_action=true">May 23, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Megha Chakraborty" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Megha Chakraborty" href="/user/show/41359514-megha-chakraborty">Megha Chakraborty</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2399148486" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17982536464451674642">One of my very good friend suggested me this book, also I wanted to explore more Japanese authors and literatures and I wasn&apos;t dissappointed. <br/>This book is about so many things, love, revenge, art, places. <br/>The writing is very abstract, still all the characters have been defined wonderfully. There is madness in all the characters, something which I cant explain for that you need to read the book. <br/>Minimalist writing is difficult and author has done it so beautifully, it was a complete page turner f</span>
  <span id="freeText17982536464451674642" style="display:none">One of my very good friend suggested me this book, also I wanted to explore more Japanese authors and literatures and I wasn't dissappointed. <br />This book is about so many things, love, revenge, art, places. <br />The writing is very abstract, still all the characters have been defined wonderfully. There is madness in all the characters, something which I cant explain for that you need to read the book. <br />Minimalist writing is difficult and author has done it so beautifully, it was a complete page turner for me. <br />Ill highly recommend this book to all. <br /><br />Happy Reading. Don’t miss on this one. <br /><br />Tata. </span>
